## Project Overview

This project is designed as a special birthday gift for Daniel Wang.

## Features

- ğŸ‚ **Cake Animation**: The cake image changes dynamically with each click, simulating the eating of a cake slice by
  slice.
- ğŸ“Š **Cake Counter**: A counter that tracks the number of cakes â€œeaten.â€
- ğŸ¥³ **Special Animation**: Every fifth cake slice triggers a special animation effect.
- ğŸ“ **GitHub Link**: A GitHub icon in the footer links to this repository.

## Getting Started

### Prerequisites

- **Node.js**: Make sure you have Node.js installed on your system. You can download it
  from [Node.js.org](https://nodejs.org/).
- **npm**: Node Package Manager is required to install dependencies.

### Installation

1. **Clone the repository:**

    ```bash
    git clone https://github.com/YuanXiQWQ/Happy-Birthday-Daniel-Wang.git
    ```

2. **Navigate to the project directory:**

    ```bash
    cd Happy-Birthday-Daniel-Wang
    ```

3. **Install the dependencies:**

    ```bash
    npm install
    ```

4. **Start the server:**

    ```bash
    node app.js
    ```

5. Open your browser and navigate to `http://localhost:3000` to view the birthday card.

